---
import '../styles/global.css';
import Logo from '../components/Logo.astro';
---

<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<meta charset="utf-8" />
		<link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
		<meta name="generator" content={Astro.generator} />
		<meta name="description" content="Micro Corp - Built by AI, Directed by Humans. Automated SaaS ecosystem part of Macro Corporate Global Alliance Oy." />
		<title>Micro Corp - The Light Side of Automation</title>
		<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
		<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
		<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700;800;900&family=Space+Grotesk:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
	</head>
	<body class="bg-slate-50 text-slate-900">
		<!-- Header -->
		<header class="absolute top-0 left-0 right-0 z-20 px-8 py-8">
			<div class="flex items-center justify-between">
				<!-- Logo Left -->
				<div class="flex items-center gap-3">
					<Logo size="40" />
					<span class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900 tracking-widest" style="font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif;">Micro Corp</span>
				</div>

				<!-- Status Right -->
				<div class="hidden md:flex items-center gap-4">
					<div class="h-4 w-[1px] bg-slate-300"></div>
					
					<div class="flex items-center gap-2">
						<span class="relative flex h-2 w-2">
							<span class="animate-ping absolute inline-flex h-full w-full rounded-full bg-blue-400 opacity-75"></span>
							<span class="relative inline-flex rounded-full h-2 w-2 bg-blue-500"></span>
						</span>
						
						<span class="text-[11px] font-mono uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-slate-500">
							System: Autonomous
						</span>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</header>

		<!-- Hero Section -->
		<section class="relative min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden">
			<!-- Glassmorphism Background Blobs -->
			<div class="absolute top-[-10%] left-[-10%] w-96 h-96 bg-blue-200 rounded-full blur-[120px] opacity-50"></div>
			<div class="absolute bottom-[-10%] right-[-10%] w-96 h-96 bg-indigo-100 rounded-full blur-[120px] opacity-50"></div>

			<div class="relative z-10 text-center px-4 max-w-6xl mx-auto">
				<h1 class="mt-4 text-6xl md:text-8xl font-extrabold text-slate-900 tracking-tighter leading-tight">
					Built by AI. <br/>
					<span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-600 to-indigo-500">
						Directed by Humans.
					</span>
				</h1>
				<p class="mt-6 text-base md:text-lg lg:text-xl text-slate-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
					Automated SaaS ecosystem. Part of Macro Corporate Global Alliance Oy. 
					We turn Macro vision into Micro execution.
				</p>
				
				<!-- CTA Buttons - COMMENTED OUT FOR FUTURE USE -->
				<!-- 
				<div class="mt-10 flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
					<a href="#products" class="px-8 py-3 bg-slate-900 text-white rounded-full font-medium hover:bg-blue-600 transition-all shadow-xl">
						Explore Products
					</a>
					<a href="#manifesto" class="px-8 py-3 bg-white/40 backdrop-blur-md border border-white/20 text-slate-900 rounded-full font-medium hover:bg-white/60 transition-all">
						Our Manifesto
					</a>
				</div>
				-->
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- Manifesto Section -->
		<section id="manifesto" class="py-20 px-4 bg-gradient-to-b from-slate-50 to-white">
			<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
				<div class="text-center mb-12">
					<h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">The Alliance Manifesto</h2>
					<p class="text-xl text-blue-600 font-semibold">Macro Vision, Micro Action.</p>
				</div>

				<div class="bg-white/40 backdrop-blur-xl rounded-xl border border-white/30 shadow-xl p-8 md:p-12 space-y-8">
					<p class="text-lg text-slate-700 leading-relaxed">
						We do not just build software. We build an autonomous ecosystem designed to transform a complex world into manageable, high-impact solutions. The world moves too fast for a single human, yet it remains too nuanced for a machine alone.
					</p>
					<p class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900">
						This is why the Alliance exists.
					</p>

					<div class="space-y-6">
						<div class="transition-all hover:translate-x-1 hover:opacity-100 opacity-90">
							<h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">1. Built by AI, Directed by Humans</h3>
							<p class="text-slate-700 leading-relaxed">
								Artificial Intelligence is our engine; the human mind is the navigator. We harness LLM models and autonomous agents to perform the heavy lifting—analyzing data, writing code, and generating content. But every bit passes through a "Human Helping Hand." We do not outsource responsibility to the machine; we multiply our capabilities through it.
							</p>
						</div>

						<div class="transition-all hover:translate-x-1 hover:opacity-100 opacity-90">
							<h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">2. The Power of the Micro</h3>
							<p class="text-slate-700 leading-relaxed mb-3">
								We believe in micro-services, micro-enterprises, and micro-steps. Micro Corp is our incubator, where ideas evolve into independent, modular tools. If a tool is valuable to us, it becomes a product for the world.
							</p>
							<ul class="space-y-2 text-slate-700">
								<li class="flex items-start gap-2">
									<span class="text-blue-600 mt-1">•</span>
								<span><strong>EditorInChief</strong> creates the content.</span>
							</li>
							<li class="flex items-start gap-2">
								<span class="text-blue-600 mt-1">•</span>
								<span><strong>OmniVocal</strong> distributes the message.</span>
								</li>
								<li class="flex items-start gap-2">
									<span class="text-blue-600 mt-1">•</span>
									<span><strong>Quillstone</strong> ensures the quality.</span>
								</li>
							</ul>
							<p class="text-slate-700 leading-relaxed mt-3">
							Together, they form the Alliance, a force greater than the sum of its parts. The Alliance continuously explores emerging satellite technologies to stay at innovation's edge.
							</p>
						</div>

						<div class="transition-all hover:translate-x-1 hover:opacity-100 opacity-90">
							<h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">3. Precision Over Noise</h3>
							<p class="text-slate-700 leading-relaxed">
							From our investment strategy to our content marketing, our principle remains the same: A <span class="text-blue-600 font-semibold">10% return</span> requires <span class="text-blue-600 font-semibold">100% precision</span>. We do not chase hype; we build sustainable "Growth Engines." As part of the Alliance, every tool and every invested euro serves the pursuit of long-term wealth and freedom.
						</p>
					</div>

					<div class="transition-all hover:translate-x-1 hover:opacity-100 opacity-90">
						<h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">4. Zero Ops, <span class="text-blue-600">Maximum Impact</span></h3>
							<p class="text-slate-700 leading-relaxed">
								Our goal is frictionless growth. We build systems that operate while we sleep—scaling on the edge with Cloudflare, free from server maintenance or unnecessary bureaucracy.
							</p>
						</div>
					</div>

					<blockquote class="border-l-4 border-blue-600 pl-6 py-2 italic text-xl text-slate-900 mt-8">
						"We don't just invest in the future. We code it."
					</blockquote>
					<p class="text-right text-slate-600 font-semibold">
						— Macro Corporate Global Alliance Oy
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- Products Section - "The Engine" -->
		<section id="products" class="py-20 px-4 max-w-7xl mx-auto">
			<div class="text-center mb-16">
				<h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">The Engine</h2>
				<p class="text-lg text-slate-600">Autonomous tools that power the Alliance</p>
			</div>

			<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-4 gap-6 auto-rows-[240px]">
				<!-- OmniVocal -->
				<a href="https://omnivocal.io" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="md:col-span-2 md:row-span-2 bg-white/40 backdrop-blur-xl rounded-xl border border-white/30 shadow-xl p-8 flex flex-col justify-between hover:scale-[1.02] transition-transform">
					<div>
						<div class="w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-br from-violet-500 to-purple-600 rounded-2xl mb-4 flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold text-xl">O</div>
						<h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">OmniVocal</h3>
						<p class="text-slate-600">Multi-platform social media distribution. Publish once, reach everywhere. The publishing engine of the Alliance.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="mt-4">
						<span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-blue-600 font-medium">
							<span class="w-2 h-2 bg-green-500 rounded-full animate-pulse"></span>
							omnivocal.io
						</span>
					</div>
				</a>

				<!-- EditorInChief -->
				<a href="https://editorinchief.io" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="md:col-span-2 bg-white/40 backdrop-blur-xl rounded-xl border border-white/30 shadow-xl p-8 flex flex-col justify-between hover:scale-[1.02] transition-transform">
					<div>
						<div class="w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-br from-indigo-500 to-blue-600 rounded-2xl mb-4 flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold text-xl">E</div>
						<h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">EditorInChief</h3>
						<p class="text-slate-600">AI content creation engine. Editorial workflow automation at scale.</p>
					</div>
					<span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-blue-600 font-medium">
						<span class="w-2 h-2 bg-green-500 rounded-full animate-pulse"></span>
						editorinchief.io
					</span>
				</a>

				<!-- PathRefine -->
				<a href="https://pathrefine.dev" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="md:col-span-1 bg-white/40 backdrop-blur-xl rounded-xl border border-white/30 shadow-xl p-8 flex flex-col justify-between hover:scale-[1.02] transition-transform">
					<div>
						<div class="w-10 h-10 bg-gradient-to-br from-emerald-500 to-teal-600 rounded-xl mb-3 flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold">P</div>
						<h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-1">PathRefine</h3>
						<p class="text-sm text-slate-600">SVG editor & optimizer</p>
					</div>
					<span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 text-xs text-emerald-600 font-medium">
						<span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-green-500 rounded-full"></span>
						Live
					</span>
				</a>

				<!-- Quillstone -->
				<a href="https://quillstone.dev" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="md:col-span-1 bg-white/40 backdrop-blur-xl rounded-xl border border-white/30 shadow-xl p-8 flex flex-col justify-between hover:scale-[1.02] transition-transform">
					<div>
						<div class="w-10 h-10 bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-500 to-pink-600 rounded-xl mb-3 flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold">Q</div>
						<h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-1">Quillstone</h3>
						<p class="text-sm text-slate-600">Content quality platform</p>
					</div>
					<span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 text-xs text-amber-600 font-medium">
						<span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-amber-500 rounded-full"></span>
						Beta
					</span>
				</a>

				<!-- SemiTruth -->
				<a href="https://semitruth.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="md:col-span-2 bg-white/40 backdrop-blur-xl rounded-xl border border-white/30 shadow-xl p-8 flex flex-col justify-between hover:scale-[1.02] transition-transform">
					<div>
						<div class="w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-br from-orange-500 to-red-600 rounded-2xl mb-4 flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold text-xl">S</div>
						<h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">SemiTruth</h3>
						<p class="text-slate-600">AI-generated satire publication. The truth is out there, SemiTruth is in here. Powered by EditorInChief & OmniVocal.</p>
					</div>
					<span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-blue-600 font-medium">
						<span class="w-2 h-2 bg-green-500 rounded-full animate-pulse"></span>
						semitruth.com
					</span>
				</a>

				<!-- Wowed -->
				<a href="https://wowed.dev" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="md:col-span-2 bg-white/40 backdrop-blur-xl rounded-xl border border-white/30 shadow-xl p-8 flex flex-col justify-between hover:scale-[1.02] transition-transform">
					<div>
						<div class="w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-br from-cyan-500 to-blue-600 rounded-2xl mb-4 flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold text-xl">W</div>
						<h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">Wowed</h3>
						<p class="text-slate-600">Get wowed. Get discovered. Social proof widget that puts builders on the map. One click from visitors, continuous discovery for you.</p>
					</div>
					<span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-emerald-600 font-medium">
						<span class="w-2 h-2 bg-green-500 rounded-full"></span>
						wowed.dev
					</span>
				</a>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- Footer -->
		<footer class="py-12 px-4 bg-slate-900 text-white">
			<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
				<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mb-8">
					<div>
						<div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
							<Logo size="40" />
							<h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold tracking-widest" style="font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif;">Micro Corp</h3>
						</div>
						<p class="text-slate-400">
							Autonomous systems for the modern era. Building the future, one micro-step at a time.
						</p>
					</div>
					<div>
						<h4 class="font-semibold mb-4">Products</h4>
						<ul class="space-y-2 text-slate-400">
						<li><a href="https://omnivocal.io" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">OmniVocal</a></li>
						<li><a href="https://editorinchief.io" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">EditorInChief</a></li>
						<li><a href="https://pathrefine.dev" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">PathRefine</a></li>
						<li><a href="https://quillstone.dev" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">Quillstone</a></li>
						<li><a href="https://semitruth.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">SemiTruth</a></li>
						<li><a href="https://wowed.dev" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">Wowed</a></li>
						</ul>
					</div>
					<div>
						<h4 class="font-semibold mb-4">Company</h4>
						<ul class="space-y-2 text-slate-400">
							<li><a href="#manifesto" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">Manifesto</a></li>
							<li><a href="#products" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">Products</a></li>
						</ul>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="border-t border-slate-800 pt-8 text-center text-slate-400">
					<p class="mb-2">
						Built by AI with a human helping hand.
					</p>
					<p>
						Part of <span class="text-white font-semibold">Micro Corp</span>, a division of 
						<span class="text-white font-semibold">Macro Corporate Global Alliance</span>.
					</p>
					<p class="mt-4 text-sm">
						© {new Date().getFullYear()} Macro Corporate Global Alliance. Taking the Macro to the Micro.
					</p>
					<p class="mt-2 text-xs font-mono text-slate-500">
						Build: 2026.02 // Status: Scaling
					</p>
					<p class="mt-3 text-[10px] font-mono text-slate-700">
						Portfolio Layer 02: Growth Engine Active
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</footer>
	</body>
</html>
